React Router v7 merged Remix directly into the router package. It works as a simple client-side router (library mode) or as a full SSR framework (framework mode). This guide focuses on framework mode — file routing, server loaders, server actions, SSR adapters, and both migration paths.

Creating a New Project

npx create-react-router@latest my-app
cd my-app
npm run dev

